# TCWT CLASS Implementation Guide
**Version:** 2026.9.2 (Single Consolidated Document)  
**Status:** Minimal, clean, and reproducible integration of TCWT into CLASS

This is a **single-file reference**. All code, instructions, and explanations are contained here. Copy the relevant sections directly into your CLASS source tree.

---

## 1. Overview

TCWT modifies CLASS in two main places:
*   Scale-dependent effective gravity $G_{\rm eff}(k,a)$
*   Additional ghost-induced $k^4$ damping in the growth equation

